            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[疑问]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yiwen-40c066d5c3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>还在喂奶的宝妈可以打HPV疫苗吗?<br><br>只能等哺乳期过了才能打👩🏻🍼。<br><br>除此之外，以下两种情况也不建议打HPV疫苗👇🏻<br>1️⃣计划生娃的女性；<br>2️⃣孕妇。<br>因为目前为止，还没有临床实验数据证明，HPV疫苗对孕妈和胎儿不会有不良影响。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#健康素养提升v计划#</span></a>（深圳疾控）<img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjlisl9f6yj20ev0eggmn.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
