            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[awsl]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fb_a3awsl-ed1a33c1b3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8F%A3%E8%87%AD%E8%85%B9%E8%83%80%E6%81%B6%E5%BF%83%E8%AD%A6%E6%83%95%E5%B9%BD%E9%97%A8%E8%9E%BA%E6%9D%86%E8%8F%8C%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8F%A3%E8%87%AD%E8%85%B9%E8%83%80%E6%81%B6%E5%BF%83%E8%AD%A6%E6%83%95%E5%B9%BD%E9%97%A8%E8%9E%BA%E6%9D%86%E8%8F%8C%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#口臭腹胀恶心警惕幽门螺杆菌感染#</span></a>】幽门螺杆菌是国际上公认与胃癌有关的致病菌，感染后患胃癌的几率会增加3到10倍<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>！医生介绍，这些症状可能在提醒你警惕：①口臭；②腹胀、腹痛；③恶心、呕吐；④非特异性消化不良。此外，不建议带14岁以下孩子常规地做幽门螺杆菌筛查👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4964337199284274" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hjizdaoucgj615z0nmb0h02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/MQnbDoG4lx089UcTXntu01041200OGOO0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1699277141&amp;ssig=jPVHyBfDtG&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/vOEYET9Zlx089UcTelEA01041200nm8K0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1699277141&amp;ssig=fq6fi6hpUc&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/8YkVzkkZlx089UcTsOiY01041200eovA0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1699277141&amp;ssig=qf%2FJjNPbvd&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4964337199284274" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
